subject: Membership
msgSnippet: I am very pleased to see that the number of members signed on to Read_Alphabet has increased by 97 in the last 6 months.  That represents a 40% increase.
messageBody:
I am very pleased to see that the number of members signed on to
Read_Alphabet has increased by 97 in the last 6 months. That
represents a 40% increase. Fantastic.

The more members we have the more likely we are to attract computer
savvy people who can help us develop better fonts, texts for
beginners,ways to use QS in our daily lives and who knows what else.
And the better our site becomes, the more likely it is to attract
people's interest. All of which will help to get the word out even more.

If you have friends whom you believe would enjoy learning about a
better way to write English, tell them about the site and invite them
to take a look at it. If you have e-mail addresses of people who
might be interested, send the addresses to me, and I'll send them an
invitation to check us out.

Thanks for all your assistance.

Paige
